title: We Have the PlayStation 5! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 10.23.20
description:
IT'S HERE. Greg and Blessing have the PS5 and are ready to do one last show before they disappear to put it through its paces this weekend .

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:04:00 - Housekeeping
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: James Davis (@JamesDavisMakes), Black Jack, & Tom Bock
The Roper Report   -
00:04:50 - WE HAVE THE PS5
00:11:20 - kid on Christmas receiving *that* package today? - Best Friends Q:Sapphire  
00:15:45 - Why does the back not have art for upcoming games to look forward to? - Best Friends Q:Madchemjst
00:20:45 -  Will you only be playing them on the new hardware and disclose as such? - Best Friends Q:The Nano Biologist
00:27:20 -  Just interested to know the process. - Best Friends Q:Adam F
00:34:20 - Xbox Getting a Streaming Stick, Tom Warren @ The Verge
00:38:30 - Now with Spencer teasing the idea of a Platinum level for GamePass, what are your thoughts - Best Friends Q:Bilbo Baginzezz
00:46:30 - While we’re talking Xcloud, Eddie @ GameSpot
00:51:35 - Ghost of Tsushima: Legends Raid, Weeklies
00:52:40 - Nintendo selling single Blue/Red Joycons in November at Discount, Owen S. Good @ Polygon
  - Miles Morales Actor Found out about Game at Launch party, Jordan Oloman @ IGN
  - Out today
  - Squad Up:Jackson S(Pokemon GO) trainer code is 782133105174
  - You‘re Wrong
Next Week’s Hosts:
MON: Blessing and Imran
TUE: Tim and Tamoor -- TIMTAM
WED: Greg and Gary
THURS: Greg and Tim
FRI: Greg and Blessing
- Post Show
